name: stress²
description:
This series of art, called «sᴛʀᴇss», is about the formation and development of stress in a person's life. Each artwork is a part of my personal experience. I hope in this you will find feelings, similar to your own worries. 
 
"Resistance. Fortitude".
 
When physical and spiritual strength are faced with anxiety, it's a good time to show fortitude.
